*Počeo* je da razmišlja o pokretanju sopstvenog biznisa. (He started to think about starting his own business.)

Sestra je *počela* da studira na univerzitetu. (The sister started to study at the university.)

*Počinje* da se približava zimskom periodu. (Winter period is starting to approach.)

Kompanija je *počela* da primenjuje nove strategije. (The company started to implement new strategies.)

*Počinjeo* je da gradi sopstveni dom. (He started to build his own house.)